#% Do not delete the line below; configure depends on this
#  \DeclareLaTeXClass[scrartcl]{article (koma-script)}
# KOMA scrartcl textclass definition file.
# Bernd Rellermeyer <100.41728@germanynet.de>, 1998/7/11.

Format 2
Input scrclass.inc
Input numarticle.inc

SecNumDepth             3
TocDepth                3

NoStyle Chapter
NoStyle Chapter*
NoStyle Addchap
NoStyle Addchap*
NoStyle Addpart
NoStyle Dictum


Style Part
	Align                 Left
	AlignPossible         Left
	TopSep                2
	BottomSep             1.5
	Font
	  Size                Larger
	EndFont
End

Style Part*
	Align                 Left
	AlignPossible         Left
	TopSep                2
	BottomSep             1.5
	Font
	  Size                Larger
	EndFont
End
